## Adding statistics

First, let's calculate summary statistics by using the code chunk below.


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
report %>% 
  group_by(Product) %>% 
  summarise("Min" = min(Sales, na.rm = T),
            "Max" = max(Sales, na.rm = T),
            "Average" = mean(Sales, na.rm = T)
            ) %>%
  gt() %>%
  fmt_number(columns = 4,
    decimals = 2)
```

